**Branch:** `loss_function`
**Status:** Idea validated; tooling built and run on real data; training integration **not yet wired**.
**This file consolidates everything in one place:** the investigation, the two scripts (`inverse_targets.py`, `demo_inverse_on_sample.py`) explained, the three ways to turn it into a loss, and exactly which files/lines to change to wire it into the MLP/joint pipeline.

---

